<bibRefCitation author="Tryon, R. M." journalOrPublisher="Fieldiana, Botany New Series" pageId="0" pageNumber="4421" pagination="1 - 176" title="Pteridophyta of Peru. Part IV. 17. Dryopteridaceae" volume="27" year="1991">Tryon et al. (1991)</bibRefCitation>
