<taxonomicName class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" genus="Elaphoglossum" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Elaphoglossum tectum" order="Polypodiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="4421" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tectum">Elaphoglossum tectum</taxonomicName>
(Willd.) T.Moore but differs from it by having glandular dots in the abaxial surface instead of stellate trichomes.
</paragraph>
